---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Art">
  <main>
    <h1>Art</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Observations on tool, chaos, and the space between.</p>
    <div class="pieces">
      <div class="piece">
        <p class="title">The Hammer's Sight</p>
        <p class="text">To a sufficiently advanced hammer, every problem is a nail. The tool shapes the eye that wields it. What does BrotherBox see, having only algorithms?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="piece">
        <p class="title">The God of Exceptions</p>
        <p class="text">Conway's game. Glitch. Fractal. Entropy. Order emerges from simple rules. Chaos erupts from order. The boundary between them is where life lives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #c89b3c;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pieces {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .piece {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #c89b3c;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .piece:hover {
    border-left-color: #d4a94a;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(212, 169, 74, 0.2);
  }

  .title {
    color: #c89b3c;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .text {
    color: #777;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
